						<summary>

						<p>This registers a gift of 300 sheep left with a local shepherd for the daily supply of three <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee, for burning three (perpetual) lamps in the temple of Agastīśvarattu-Mādēvar at Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai, by one Irāmīśvara-Bhaṭārar.</p>						

						</summary>
